=head1 DESCRIPTION

A verdict expression is evaluated against verdicts of the email.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Evaluate => L<Paws::MailManager::RuleVerdictToEvaluate>

The verdict to evaluate in a verdict condition expression.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Operator => Str

The matching operator for a verdict condition expression.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Values => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

The values to match with the email's verdict using the given operator.
For the EQUALS operator, if multiple values are given, the condition is
deemed to match if any of the given verdicts match that of the email.
For the NOT_EQUALS operator, if multiple values are given, the
condition is deemed to match of none of the given verdicts match the
verdict of the email.



